info:
Job Description:

*Support APAC SAP-EHS community on SAP EHS system implementation, continuous improvement. Mailing MSDS to customer, maintain customer email address.
*Support Regulatory Affairs colleague handle on regular works.
*Provide administrative support to the PSRA Dept. on other global and regional coordination work.

Requirement:

*Bachelor degree or above in chemical or HSE related area is preferred;
*be innovative, persistent and committed to a successful completion of assignments on-time with complete accuracy;
*Communication skills to ensure those internal requirements and customers’ needs are understood;
*Chinese and very good English;
*At least work 3 days per week, at least 4 months
